title: Recall Notification Report 041-2016 (Pork Dumpling Products)
summary: WASHINGTON, May 18, 2016 Aurnish Enterprises Corporation, a Woodside, N.Y. establishment, is recalling approximately 5,616 pounds of pork dumpling products due to misbranding, the U.S. Department of Agricultures Food Safety and Inspection Service (FSIS) announced today.
